## Current Scope

This version is designed to be a strong MVP:

- it focuses on multicopter rate-loop tuning
- it supports offline analysis only
- it produces explainable recommendations
- it does not attempt direct flight-controller writes

## Next Steps

- add richer ULog topic mapping for more PX4 airframes
- add multi-log joint identification
- add actuator saturation and filter recommendation models
- integrate SITL or Gazebo-based replay validation
